		opt1 := "running"
		status, err := servicemesh.GetServiceMeshes(ctx, &servicemesh.GetServiceMeshesArgs{
			Ids: []string{
				"example_id",
			},
			Status: &opt1,
		}, nil)
		if err != nil {
			return err
		}
		ctx.Export("serviceMeshServiceMeshId3", status.Meshes[0].Id)
		return nil
	})
